Installation 

If access to apache server is not available, is good to download MAMP free version. However, it is an html file so it will run on any browser. 

It is very easy since is only one page that can be scalable to new features.
Variables use meaningful names, classes use appropriate naming conventions.  
The only situation that will make this code time consuming will be to transition from the API  to sql . However, this will add a better performance. 
Also, the library is open source can be use without any additional expense. 


 There are several validation points that help debugging faster and more intuitive.  All validation points contain a clear structure and execute accordingly.

